<item>
            <title>[LU-8713] Load zfs modules during libzfs_init</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8713</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Between 0.6.5.7 and 0.6.5.8 (and also on master prior to 0.7.0-rc1) Systemd configuration was changed such that, zfs kernel module was not loaded automatically, but only on zfs-import-*.service.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;zfs-0.6.5-release:  6ae855d8a75133b9a5124287bfa3d5a41bb32c15&lt;br/&gt;
master: 92547bc45ca9a2114662d9343ae53e5098acb627&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This breaks autotest, and doesn&apos;t necessarily make sense for all lustre use cases.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
